These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, nurse, dancer
1. the nurse is on the far left##1
2. the pilot is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | nurse | dancer | pilot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, coach, security-guard
1. the security-guard is on the far right##1
2. the manager is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | manager | coach | security-guard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, collecting, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
