1. the argentine is on the far right##1
2. the argentine is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | italian | spanish | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, lemonade
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | coffee | milk | lemonade |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, roller
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | roller | helicopter | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, superhero, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | romance | superhero |

 #################################

 
